The wallpaper (wallpaper/cirno.jpeg) depicts Cirno, a character from the
Touhou Project by Team Shanghai Alice (ZUN). The artwork is by azumammeri
(https://x.com/azumammeri/status/1487768625666994178). Touhou Project fan works
are permitted under ZUN's guidelines for non-commercial, derivative use. The
wallpaper is included for personal theming use and is NOT covered by the MIT
license above; all rights to the artwork and to the Touhou Project belong to
their respective creators.
